OL,3,CCoroner warns of e-bike dangers after
OL,4,Cboy dies in fire
OL,6,FA coroner has called for greater
OL,7,Fpublic awareness of the "life-
OL,8,Fthreatening" risks of storing
OL,9,Felectronic bikes and scooters in the
OL,10,Fhome after an eight-year-old boy died
OL,11,Ffollowing a house fire caused by an e-
OL,12,Fbike.
OL,14,FLuke Albiston O'Donnell died in
OL,15,Fhospital from hypoxia ` low levels of
OL,16,Foxygen in the body ` and carbon
OL,17,Fmonoxide poisoning after charging e-
OL,18,Fbike caught alight in his house in
OL,19,FBirkenhead, Merseyside, an inquest
OL,20,Fconcluded.
