OL,3,CCoroner warns of e-bike dangers after
OL,4,Cboy dies in fire
OL,6,FIn June, a coroner called for
OL,7,FGovernment action after the death of a
OL,8,Fman whose home in Bristol caught fire
OL,9,Fwhen an e-bike battery pack he was
OL,10,Fcharging overheated and ignited.
OL,12,FMaria Voisin, senior coroner for Avon,
OL,13,Fissued the plea after presiding over
OL,14,Fan inquest into the death of Abdul
OL,15,FOryakhel who fell from the window of
OL,16,Fhis 16th floor flat while trying to
OL,17,Fescape the blaze.
