OL,3,CCoroner warns of e-bike dangers after
OL,4,Cboy dies in fire
OL,6,FAlso in June, grieving father Scott
OL,7,FPeden, 30, from Cambridge, called for
OL,8,Furgent e-bike safety measures one year
OL,9,Fafter his partner and two children
OL,10,Fdied in a fire.
OL,12,FMr Peden lost his partner Gemma, 31,
OL,13,Fand their children Lilly, eight, and
OL,14,FOliver, four, during a fire caused by
OL,15,Fan e-bike battery bought online.
