OL,3,CCoroner warns of e-bike dangers after
OL,4,Cboy dies in fire
OL,6,FThe latest warning from Ms Bhardwaj
OL,7,Fcomes after the Department for
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade (DBT) urged
OL,9,Fconsumers in October to avoid buying e-
OL,10,Fbikes and e-scooters from rogue online
OL,11,Fsellers because of the risk of deadly
OL,12,Ffires.
OL,14,FThe DBT said faulty parts have
OL,15,Fresulted in hundreds of incidents
OL,16,Facross the UK where the electric
OL,17,Fmobility devices have caught fire,
OL,18,Fsome of which have resulted in deaths.
