OL,3,CCoroner warns of e-bike dangers after
OL,4,Cboy dies in fire
OL,6,FLondon Fire Brigade said it attended
OL,7,F143 e-bike fires and 36 e-scooter
OL,8,Fblazes last year, causing a total of
OL,9,Fthree deaths and leaving around 60
OL,10,Fpeople injured.
OL,12,FThe DBT launched a campaign calling on
OL,13,Fthe public to buy only safe products
OL,14,Ffrom reputable sellers, only replace
OL,15,Fparts with products recommended by the
OL,16,Fmanufacturer, and seek professional
OL,17,Fhelp when converting or repairing e-
OL,18,Fbikes or e-scooters.
